.TH "HPC\-COMPOSE\-DOCTOR" "1" "" "hpc\-compose 0.1.33" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
hpc\-compose\-doctor \- Check cluster readiness and tool availability
.SH SYNOPSIS
.nf
hpc\-compose doctor [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]
.fi
.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
Run environment diagnostics without requiring a compose file. Checks Slurm, runtime backend tools, GPU, and cache directory availability. Use the cluster\-report, mpi\-smoke, and fabric\-smoke subcommands for targeted probes.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBcluster\-report\fR
Generate a best\-effort cluster capability profile. See hpc\-compose\-doctor\-cluster\-report(1).
.TP
\fBmpi\-smoke\fR
Render or run an MPI smoke probe for one service. See hpc\-compose\-doctor\-mpi\-smoke(1).
.TP
\fBfabric\-smoke\fR
Render or run MPI and fabric smoke probes for one service. See hpc\-compose\-doctor\-fabric\-smoke(1).
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB--format\fR \fIFORMAT\fR
Output format. Possible values: text, json.
.TP
\fB--sbatch\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the sbatch executable. Default: sbatch.
.TP
\fB--srun\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the srun executable. Default: srun.
.TP
\fB--scontrol\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the scontrol executable. Default: scontrol.
.TP
\fB--enroot\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the enroot executable. Default: enroot.
.TP
\fB--apptainer\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the apptainer executable. Default: apptainer.
.TP
\fB--singularity\-bin\fR \fIPATH\fR
Path to the singularity executable. Default: singularity.
.TP
\fB--color\fR \fIWHEN\fR
Controls colored output. Default: auto. Possible values: auto, always, never.
.TP
\fB--quiet\fR
Suppress progress indicators and non\-essential labels.
.TP
\fB--profile\fR \fINAME\fR
Profile name to load from .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB--settings\-file\fR \fIPATH\fR
Explicit settings file path; defaults to upward search for .hpc\-compose/settings.toml.
.TP
\fB-h\fR, \fB--help\fR
Print help (see a summary with '\-h').
.SH EXAMPLES
.nf
hpc\-compose doctor
hpc\-compose doctor cluster\-report
hpc\-compose doctor mpi\-smoke \-f compose.yaml \-\-service trainer
hpc\-compose doctor fabric\-smoke \-f compose.yaml \-\-service trainer \-\-checks auto
.fi
